abstract: College football's top-ranked Louisiana State defeats Auburn, 45-10, to remain undefeated at 8-0.
snippet: Top-ranked Louisiana State’s rout of 19th-ranked Auburn Saturday set the stage for the most anticipated game of the season — a showdown with No. 2 Alabama on Nov. 5 in Tuscaloosa, Ala.
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Louisiana State’s rout of 19th-ranked Auburn Saturday set the stage for the most anticipated game of the season — a showdown with No. 2 Alabama on Nov. 5 in Tuscaloosa, Ala.

headline.main: L.S.U. Is Not Slowed on Road to Showdown
headline.print_headline: L.S.U. Blows Past Auburn on the Road to a Showdown With Alabama
headline.seo: L.S.U. Routs Auburn, Last Season’s National Champion
